<div><h1></h1><p></p><br /></div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="panel-heading">
        <p>Select File ( <a asp-action="Download" title="Click for download" asp-route-id="LoanMedicalTemplate.xlsx">Download Template</a>) :</p>
    </div>
